    "updated_at": "2016-12-05T09:44:26Z",
    "body": "@MarshallOfSound, I just want to remind you that a move is not affected by copy speed within the same disk partition. I would also point out that it's probably not very common for users to have \"$HOME/.config/\" and \"$HOME/.cache/\" on different partitions, in which case the copy speed would be a factor.\r\n\r\nI am not denying that it can cause issues, although it's not clear for me what those issues really are, and if they are real or not..."
