    "created_at": "2017-04-22T06:31:45Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-04-22T06:37:30Z",
    "body": "> with their default values set to the current locations? \r\n\r\nNot sure this makes sense. A big part of the XDG specification is it's definition for defaults. However, if there was a ELECTRON_USE_XDG the user could set, that would be a good start.\r\n\r\nUPDATE: And a way for apps to do the same of course."
  },
